---
  <section
    id="experience"
    class="grid grid-cols-1 items-center gap-10 bg-dark-red px-5 py-20 md:gap-20 md:px-10 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:px-20 lg:py-20"
  >
    <div class="exp-left">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-[clamp(30px,3.5vw,48px)] font-light leading-tight text-cream">
        Every Feast is a <em class="italic">Carefully Composed</em> Story
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-[440px] font-body text-xl leading-[1.85] text-cream/70">
        We believe that catering is not merely feeding — it is the art of creating an atmosphere, a memory, an emotion.
        Our team of master chefs, event specialists, and service professionals work in seamless choreography to bring
        your vision to life.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-11 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-7">
        <a href="/about" class="btn-cream">Our Philosophy</a>
        <a href="#" class="btn-ghost text-blush">How We Work</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-0.5 sm:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="bg-cream/5 px-6 py-7">
        <span class="mb-2 block font-body text-[10px] tracking-[0.25em] text-blush uppercase">Cuisine</span>
        <span class="font-serif text-xl italic leading-snug text-cream"
          >Indian, International & Fusion — from Rajasthani dals to Mediterranean mezze</span
        >
      </div>
      <div class="bg-cream/5 px-6 py-7">
        <span class="mb-2 block font-body text-[10px] tracking-[0.25em] text-blush uppercase">Presentation</span>
        <span class="font-serif text-xl italic leading-snug text-cream"
          >Editorial plating and live station theatre that commands attention</span
        >
      </div>
      <div class="bg-cream/5 px-6 py-7">
        <span class="mb-2 block font-body text-[10px] tracking-[0.25em] text-blush uppercase">Reach</span>
        <span class="font-serif text-xl italic leading-snug text-cream"
          >Pan India deployment with full logistics — Pune, Mumbai, Delhi, Goa &amp; beyond</span
        >
      </div>
      <div class="bg-cream/5 px-6 py-7">
        <span class="mb-2 block font-body text-[10px] tracking-[0.25em] text-blush uppercase">Bespoke</span>
        <span class="font-serif text-xl italic leading-snug text-cream"
          >Custom menus built around your event, dietary needs, and cultural traditions</span
        >
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
